#: persons-identity.rst:4
msgid "The :ref:`person` claim type describes basic identifying information about a :ref:`person`: their name, aliases and associated time ranges with them. Claims of this type are grouped together with :ref:`Posting` (describing postings to different units) which tracks the person's career. There are also several fields in development to capture other aspects about persons."
msgstr ""

